article_id:1545,category_name:Events,title_name:A New Facility Event, Agents of the Goddess, Is Coming Soon!,image_path:https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1c727c549f8a1ecc64926aed2044e71f.png,message:<div>A new facility event, Agents of the Goddess, will begin <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1598594400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>This event will pit your group of adventurers against bosses of the light element. You&#39;ll also be able to get an event-related reward facility!</div><div><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/1c727c549f8a1ecc64926aed2044e71f.png"></div><div>People and fiends alike are suddenly going berserk, much to the confusion of the prince and friends. That&#39;s when self-proclaimed apostles arrive from the north and beseech the prince and his allies to aid in their mission. Whatever the motives of the foes who lurk behind this phenomenon may be, this story will be the preface that plunges our heroes into the unknown!</div><div><br></div><div>â– Event Duration</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1598594400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1599803999"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign to participate.</div><div>2. Players must have completed up to Chapter 2 / 2-1 (Normal) of the main campaign in order to play co-op.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1598335200,update_time1598263697